script.params:
params positions transfer to script in same order. example: exec_path input_file output_file solvent temperature user can use more params. but only required and optional will be replaced by value from db
input_file Path to file that contains mol data. input_file - is a required field name
output_file Path to file which contains result data. Result data should be in JSON format. Example: {"predicted_value":"777","applicability_domain":"true"} output_file - is a required field name
solvent Solvent name, is a optional field.
temperature temperature (Celsius), is a optional field
